# are served directly. Any other path falls through to the app shell and the
# client router renders the 404, instead of Cloudflare's unbranded default.
# Real static files (robots.txt, sitemap.xml, /assets/*, brand images) and the
# prerendered route folders are all served before this rule.
/*  /index.html  200
